Web mapping   Data analysis  Data visualization  Computer vision  ObjectOriented Programming  Specifically the 10 Python applications you will build are  A program that returns Englishword definitions emails Analyze and visualize data Use Python to schedule programs based on computer events Learn OOP ObjectOriented Programming Learn GUIs GraphicalUser Interfaces Are there any course requirements or
